  <brief_title>A Prospective Active-Reference Study of Gaboxadol in Primary Insomnia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomised Double-Blind Parallel-Group Placebo-Controlled Active-Reference Study of Gaboxadol in Primary Insomnia</official_title>
